title: 100,000+ voters reached this election cycle by PV22
description:
We are proud to have mobilized our activist network of over 7000 individuals to sign up for over 1000 events, reaching out to over 100,000 voters during this election cycle. None of this would have been possible without the tireless efforts of our dedicated volunteers. Thank you for your hard work and dedication. We look forward to continuing the fight for a better future with you in the year ahead.

title: Making Every State BLUE in 2022 with EveryDistrict
description:
Some of the most decisions happen at the state level and yet we systematically underestimate the importance of our state legislatures. Nicole Hobbs, Co-Founder of EveryDistrict, comes to the Progressive Victory community to teach our members why it's important to get involved at the state level and why it's critical to turn those legislatures blue. 

Join PV22: https://progressivevictory.win/volunteer

title: Win in the PA State House with Paul Takac
description: Democratic State House candidate Paul Takac joined us to speak about what's at stake in PA's 2022 election and how smaller, under-the-radar races like his can have profound impacts on LGBTQ+ rights, abortion rights, and the freedom to vote for millions of people. He is running in a district where student turnout will determine the outcome.
